# Forward PWAs still re-fetching the old hashed manifest URL (now gone)
# to the stable path. `_redirects` fire even when no asset matches.
# Removable in ~a month, once most installs have refreshed.
#
# Anchor the match to the `.webmanifest` extension: a bare `manifest-*`
# splat also swallows hashed route chunks like `manifest-route-<hash>.js`
# (301'd to JSON, they break the gallery's dynamic import). The `:hash`
# placeholder matches any non-`/` run — hyphenated hashes included — while
# the trailing literal keeps it scoped to the old manifest asset.
/_build/assets/manifest-:hash.webmanifest  /manifest.webmanifest  301
